name: Maga
description:
Title: "Maga"
Serie: "El Mundo"
Year 2020


Externally this painting shows how "Maga" starts developing a new conscious,and how under the influence of the inner sun she can break free from the cold net that had trapped herself.
Internally "Maga" is a reflection of my first steps in a whole new world, of how my feminine inner part starts gaining power, allowing me to work on myself and reach new states of being..
"Maga" shows the impact that different women had have on my life and how in their role of iniciators they have completely transformed my conception of the world.

"If it were no me, who would be the foundation of my kingdom. I am the guardian of the treasure, the bitch that defends the hidden sun with her life"

Acrylic painting 110x80cm
